@marcofalke

> I know this is off-topic, but are the translations for the website synced regularly? If not, it doesn't seem worth it to keep them there.

BitcoinCore.org doesn't use the Transifex infrastructure currently (I'm not sure it ever did).  Translations for the website are currently submitted via normal PRs, which works for me, so I'm good with dropping them from Transifex.
